Through everything I’ve had to endure, you and this blog have truly kept me going. The responsibility I feel for this community I created gave me a reason to get up in the morning. Having this website saved my life, both emotionally and financially and I will be eternally grateful. I’m determined to take what will hopefully be the worst thing that has ever happened to me, and turn it into the best thing that could have ever happened.
